short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A browser extension by SeaFloor that lets you check the latest stats for your NFTs.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Latest SeaFloor extension that will allow users to check latest status for NFTs at OpenSea. It will show the rarity score and rank and its trading volume, and so much more.
